This is just a prototype !!
It uses the formidable plugin by felixge (http://github.com/felixge/node-formidable) and the jquery.iframe-post-form.js (http://jquery.malsup.com/form/) plugin. 

== Improvments

* websocks (only on google chrome). longpoling a mere hack http://armstrongonsoftware.blogspot.com/2009/12/comet-is-dead-long-live-websockets.html
* jquery ui - an animated progress bar
